<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Deputation" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Deputation,</orth> the office of a substitute, vicegerency: <bibl n="shak. mm 1.1.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 1, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.1.32" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 1, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.3.87" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.13.74" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 13, 74</bibl> (O. Edd. <emph>disputation</emph>). <cit><quote>thy topless d. he puts on,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.152" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 152</bibl></cit>, i. e. thy dignity as Jove's substitute; cf. <emph>deputy</emph> in <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.221" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 221</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 3.1.136" default="NO" valid="yes">John III, 1, 136</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 2, 38</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>